The paper discusses a next-generation research and discovery platform for scholarly publications, grants, patents, and clinical trials. This suggests that the paper may belong to the Digital Libraries (cs.DL) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of citation indexing and expansion, which falls under Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI). Additionally, the paper may be relevant to the sub-categories of Cybersecurity (cs.CY) and Computation and Language (cs.CL) as it discusses the potential benefits of the platform for policy makers and the general public.
